<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4736463>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 5. A maximum likelihood-based phylogenetic tree of the families Antipathidae and Aphanipathidae based on mitochondrial cox3-cox1 sequence data (Chery et al. 2018). The original tree consisted of 84 taxa and 1,111 sites and was rooted to anemones and zoanthids. PhyML used the GTR+I+G model of sequence evolution and 1,000 bootstrap replicates." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4736463/files/figure.png" .

